{"type":2},"type":"arrow","updated":1776128389395,"id":"VNrwgo3ek_wS3afRBT6Xn","x":912.56466317889965,"seed":831011499,"boundElements":[],"y":2468.9407871181488,"opacity":100,"height":79.319175130165604,"points":[[0,0],[95.513283973505168,79.319175130165604]],"width":95.513283973505168,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":495607627},{"seed":797864043,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xb3LloHvJhDB3KitNoLJq","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":2,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1776128598980,"locked":false,"text":"In Redis, keys decide how data is distributed across\ndifferent nodes in a cluster. So, how you design your\nkeys directly affects how your data is organized and\nhow well your system can scale.\n","version":151,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","index":"aX","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"In Redis, keys decide how data is distributed across different nodes in a cluster. So, how you design your keys directly affects how your data is organized and how well your system can scale.\n","height":125,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":503862789,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1134.2284117302333,"angle":0,"y":2758.6374484094044,"width":521.1033493857808},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness":2,"groupIds":[],"index":"aY","backgroundColor":"transparent","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":218,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1776129723688,"id":"2xSVk2e9TOGootB6igXTU","x":551.02436067279723,"seed":312852619,"boundElements":[],"y":1570.323510173979,"opacity":100,"height":1413.6132369272366,"width":1233.0810363760677,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"dotted","versionNonce":1100047077},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","link":null,"roughness":2,"groupIds":[],"index":"aZ","b